wpt.desc: Shrek by MF trackers, Traditional Cache (1.5/2)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Shrek
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: Skrek and Fiona's favorite hideout. Bring a quill and ink. Will be muddy after a rain. Not on 476 no matter what your GPS says
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description: You are looking for a plastic cammo jar. 1.5 inch high and 1 inch wide. It has a log scroll and room for very, very small objects. It is not hidden on private property.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:encoded_hints:
Hint 1: Where do Ogre's hide
Hint 2: Up against the wall and spread em

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Found with dawnie22 and our girls.
